PrecisEnactment of REGULATIONS AMENDING THE CITIZENSHIP REGULATIONS, 1993 which increase fees for the processing of an application for a change in citizenship status, for the granting, the retaining and registering, the renunciation and the resumption of citizenship under sections 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 and 8, and for the processing of applications for citizenship status documents and searches.
